  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<div>We're thrilled to announce that next week&nbsp;we’ll be launching a&nbsp;<strong data-stringify-type=\"bold\">new release path for Analytics Client JS</strong>, upgrading from&nbsp;<strong data-stringify-type=\"bold\">version 1.1.10 to 1.1.11</strong>.<br>\nAlso, we'd like to announce that today we're launching the same patch (1.1.11) for Internal customers.<br>\nThis release includes important fixes for the following tickets:&nbsp;</div>\n\n<ul data-border=\"0\" data-indent=\"0\" data-list-tree=\"true\" data-stringify-type=\"unordered-list\">\n\t<li data-list-item-id=\"ef70363a29de5db223964aba9f60929aa\" data-stringify-border=\"0\" data-stringify-indent=\"0\"><a data-sk=\"tooltip_parent\" data-stringify-link=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LPD-59247\" href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LPD-59247\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">LPD-59247</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div><span aria-label=\"&nbsp;\" data-stringify-type=\"paragraph-break\"></span><span data-qa=\"emoji\" data-sk=\"tooltip_parent\"><img alt=\":clock1:\" aria-label=\"clock1 emoji\" data-stringify-emoji=\":clock1:\" data-stringify-type=\"emoji\" height=\"22\" src=\"https://a.slack-edge.com/production-standard-emoji-assets/14.0/google-medium/1f550@2x.png\" width=\"22\"></span> <strong data-stringify-type=\"bold\">Release Schedule in PROD:</strong></div>\n\n<ul data-border=\"0\" data-indent=\"0\" data-list-tree=\"true\" data-stringify-type=\"unordered-list\">\n\t<li data-list-item-id=\"e2c12685a930bb6ce1dc182241a2a93c4\" data-stringify-border=\"0\" data-stringify-indent=\"0\">&nbsp;The release will be performed at&nbsp;<strong data-stringify-type=\"bold\">1:00 PM PST on July 17th</strong></li>\n</ul>"
      },
